show.description:
After a painful divorce, a once-silent wife returns fiercer than ever—shaking the elite with her rise to power. From humiliation to dominance, she takes down those who wronged her, one by one.
A revenge-fueled saga of strength, transformation, and the brutal cost of underestimating a woman.
